<title><![CDATA[Gomen - Spinach with Homemade Cheese]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[This is one of the most delicious ways I know to eat spinach. Spicy, buttery and nutty, I could eat endless bowls full of gomen without tiring.]]></description>
<source/>
<img></img>
